-stock-pikachu-card-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/pokemon-van-gogh-museum-will-no-longer-stock-pikachu-card-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/pokemon-van-gogh-museum-will-no-longer-stock-pikachu-card-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/pokemon-van-gogh-museum-will-no-longer-stock-pikachu-card-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/pokemon-van-gogh-museum-will-no-longer-stock-pikachu-card-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>梵高博物馆（Van Gogh Museum）的几名员工因声称他们偷走了<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/pokemon">神奇宝贝</a>卡而被暂停。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/game-reviews/like-a-dragon-infinite-wealth-review-3575086">“像龙：无限财富”评论：夏威夷冒险在阳光下提供一切</a></strong></li></ul><p>据<em><a href="https://www.parool.nl/amsterdam/vier-medewerkers-van-gogh-museum-weg-na-wangedrag-bij-pokemonexpo~be629fc7/?referrer=https://t.co/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Het Parool</a></em> （通过<em><a href="https://www.dexerto.com/pokemon/pokemon-cards-reportedly-stolen-from-van-gogh-museum-by-several-employees-2494330/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Dexerto</a> ）</em>报道，在“展览不当行为”之后，博物馆中至少有四名员工被停职。在<em>Dexerto</em>提供的<em>Het Parool</em>文章的翻译中，声称其中一名员工“雇用了25年”，并且他们不遵守博物馆工作人员的“程序和行为守则”。</p><p>梵高博物馆的神奇宝贝展览<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/pokemon-and-van-gogh-museum-reveal-limited-edition-pikachu-card-3505908">于去年9月开始</a>，并于今年1月关闭。它的特色是梵高主题的皮卡丘卡，可供购买特殊的van Gogh和PokémonCollection购买，这些卡很快就成为了众多的收藏家商品。 </p><figure id="attachment_3515703" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3515703" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3515703" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/pokemon-van-gogh-museum-will-no-longer-stock-pikachu-card-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/pokemon-van-gogh-museum-will-no-longer-stock-pikachu-card-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/pokemon-van-gogh-museum-will-no-longer-stock-pikachu-card-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/pokemon-van-gogh-museum-will-no-longer-stock-pikachu-card-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/pokemon-van-gogh-museum-will-no-longer-stock-pikachu-card-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/pokemon-van-gogh-museum-will-no-longer-stock-pikachu-card-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/pokemon-van-gogh-museum-will-no-longer-stock-pikachu-card-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3515703" class="wp-caption-text"> “PokémonXVan Gogh”博物馆画廊信用：神奇宝贝公司</figcaption></figure><p>由于“安全与保障”的问题，这些卡后来<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/van-gogh-pikachu-pokemon-card-pulled-from-museum-amid-safety-concerns-3515622">在10月停产</a>。</p><p>一份<a href="https://www.vangoghmuseum.nl/en/about/collaborate/van-gogh-museum-brand-licenses/collaboration-license-partners/van-gogh-museum-x-pokemon#frequently-asked-questions">声明</a>说：“梵高博物馆和国际<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/the-pokemon-company">神奇宝贝公司</a>非常重视游客和员工的安全。”</p><p> “最近，一小群人造成了不良情况，这使我们做出了艰难的决定，将皮卡丘用灰色毡帽促销卡从博物馆中删除。这样，游客将能够以安全而愉快的方式体验这些特别的神奇宝贝绘画和博物馆的收藏。”</p><p>根据<em>Het Parool的</em>说法，据称一名雇员挪用了其中一盒，博物馆发言人向出口确认该事件目前正在进行并正在进行中，并且根据几个消息来源，其他员工正在帮助游客购买门票对于卡片。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中，开发商<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/fntastic">Fntastic</a><em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/the-day-before">的前一天</a></em>ca <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/the-day-before-developer-claims-hate-campaign-sank-controversial-game-3576233">表示，“仇恨运动”</a>在一份长度上沉没了游戏。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/van-gogh-museum-employees-suspended-over-pokemon-incident-3576268">梵高博物馆的邮政员工暂停了“神奇宝贝”的“事件”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
